properties.Name: DunBradstreetPaymentSummary
properties.Description: Payment summary information for payments received by industry.

Columns.Name: DunsNumber
Columns.Description: Dun & Bradstreet (D&B) provides a D-U-N-S Number, a unique nine digit identification number, for each physical location of your business.

Columns.Name: ReportPurchaseDate
Columns.Description: The purchase date of the report.

Columns.Name: NumberOfPaymentsReceived
Columns.Description: The number of payments received from that industry.

Columns.Name: TotalDollarAmountOfPaymentsReceived
Columns.Description: The total dollar amount of payments received from the industry.

Columns.Name: HighestCreditAmount
Columns.Description: The highest credit amount extended to the industry.

Columns.Name: PercentageWithinTerms
Columns.Description: The percentage of payments received that were within terms.

Columns.Name: NumberDaysSlowLessThan31Days
Columns.Description: The number of payments received that were slow less than 31 days.

Columns.Name: NumberDaysSlow3160Days
Columns.Description: The number of payments received that were slow 31-60 days.

Columns.Name: NumberDaysSlow6190Days
Columns.Description: The number of payments received that were slow 61-90 days.

Columns.Name: NumberDaysSlowGreaterThan90Days
Columns.Description: The number of payments received that were greater than 90 days

Columns.Name: DunBradstreetIndustryTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Dun Bradstreet industry type.
